      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures including version-controlled release notes, regression test suite, and FDA-recognized software development lifecycle documentation. SQA level 2 is commensurate with MRL 2.",
