      "rationale": "Systematic mesh convergence study performed on three mesh levels (1.2M, 3.8M, 9.6M cells) using Richardson extrapolation. GCI values of 1.8–2.3% for wall shear stress QOI across all five operating points. Exceeds Gradation 2 requirement; Gradation 3 achieved through formal GCI analysis with monotonic convergence confirmed.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
