        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "GCI < 5% for primary QOI on finest mesh relative to Richardson-extrapolated value. Monotonic convergence demonstrated across at least three mesh levels. Gradation 3 requires formal GCI quantification per Roache methodology."
