      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, hematocrit, temperature, inlet pressure) were measured with calibrated instrumentation and are documented in the test report. Boundary conditions applied in CFD match experimental conditions within ±2% for all five validation operating points within the declared envelope.",
