      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison of CFD-predicted RH index against experimental measurements across all five operating points. Maximum absolute error of 4.1%; all predictions within combined experimental and numerical uncertainty bands. Validation metric (E = |RH_pred - RH_exp| / RH_exp) < 5% at all points.",
