      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence, numerical solver error beyond discretization error and code verification is scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 factor applicability table. The commercially validated solver provides sufficient assurance at this risk level; iterative convergence to residuals < 1e-6 is documented for all runs and subsumes solver error assessment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this Class II application. The CFD analysis is performed by experienced analysts with documented training records, and the simulation workflow is controlled under a documented SOPs. Formal use error assessment is reserved for MRL 3 and above per organizational credibility planning."
