      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification beyond the sensitivity analysis performed on hemolysis model coefficients is scoped out at MRL 2. The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is the established standard for CFD hemolysis prediction; coefficient sensitivity is documented in the uncertainty quantification records. Full model form assessment is deferred to MRL 3 activities."
    },
    {
