      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty propagation beyond the Monte Carlo analysis documented in the validation uncertainty quantification records is scoped out at MRL 2. Key inputs (viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) have documented nominal values and uncertainty ranges; propagation results are captured in the validation result UQ objects."
