      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Detailed test sample characterization (e.g., donor variability, batch-to-batch blood property variation) is scoped out at MRL 2. The validation experiments used a consistent porcine blood source with hematocrit controlled to 35 ± 1.5%, which is within the declared applicability constraint. Sample characterization beyond this level is appropriate for MRL 3."
